### Development
```fish
# Node.js projects
pnpm dev                # Start development server
pnpm test               # Run tests
pnpm build              # Build for production

# Ruby projects
rails server            # Start Rails server (if Rails)
bundle exec rspec       # Run RSpec tests
bundle exec rubocop     # Run code linter
```

